Implement a robust Reminders & Notifications system for QuestHabit that delivers scheduled reminders for habits via push notifications (FCM for Android/Web Push, APNs for iOS), with optional email fallback, and an in-app Notification Center. The system supports user-configurable channels (push, email), quiet hours, time zone-aware scheduling, retry/backoff strategies, and a server-side scheduler. UI components include a Notifications Center, Habit Detail, and Settings & Preferences pages. All code must defensively guard against null/undefined values for arrays and API results, and initialize React state with proper defaults for arrays/objects.

